        </item>
        <item>
            <title>日本推出多功能蓝牙 Cassette 机，可听收音机、转录 Cassette 带成 MP3</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/15/japanese-bluetooth-cassette/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=japanese-bluetooth-cassette</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/15/japanese-bluetooth-cassette/wireless-home/audio-visual/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 11:00:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音产品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Cassette]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[卡式带]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[收音机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[蓝牙喇叭]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1275331</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本 SANWA 近日推出一款具备多功能的蓝牙收音机 400-MEDI050BK，结合传统与现代技术，为用户提供全方位音讯体验。除了可以播放卡式带，更支援 AM/FM 收音机功能，另外具备蓝牙连接，甚至更可将卡带播转换为数码格式，兼具怀旧与实用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275364" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_01-600x580.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_01-600x580.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_01.jpg 931w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 600px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275365" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_02-501x580.jpg" alt="" width="501" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_02-501x580.jpg 501w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_02.jpg 777w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 501px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275362" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_09-694x325.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="325" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_09-694x325.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_09.jpg 1045w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275363" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_10-493x580.jpg" alt="" width="493" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_10-493x580.jpg 493w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_10.jpg 765w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 493px" /></p><p>这款收音机可播放卡式带功能，更能够将音讯转换为 MP3 格式，并储存至 USB 手指或 SD 卡中。其蓝牙功能允许与手机或其他装置连接，用户可轻松播放现代串流音乐。此外，装置亦有 MP3 播放器，提供多样化的音乐播放选项。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275357" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_04-392x580.jpg" alt="" width="392" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_04-392x580.jpg 392w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_04.jpg 608w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 392px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可以将卡式带转录为 MP3 档案</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275358" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_05-581x580.jpg" alt="" width="581" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_05-581x580.jpg 581w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_05.jpg 901w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_05-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 581px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最快仅需要 6 个步骤即可完成转录</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275360" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_07-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_07-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_07.jpg 1045w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可转录至 SD 卡、USB 手指等</p><p>装置设计上体积轻便，方便携带，在电源方面，这部卡式机可以使用电芯或交流电两种供电方式，无论是室内居家享受还是户外派对均可应对，用户无需为电力供应或音源格式担忧。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275361" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_08-551x580.jpg" alt="" width="551" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_08-551x580.jpg 551w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_08.jpg 855w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 551px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲支援电芯及交流电</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275359" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_06-694x505.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="505" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_06-694x505.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_06.jpg 1045w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可充当蓝牙喇叭</p><p>这款收音机售价为 13,800 日元（约港币 690 元），颜色方面可选择黑色或红色，收音机以其怀旧外观和现代功能成为家庭和旅游爱好者的理想选择。产品结合经典收音机的质感与现代技的便利，为音乐爱好者和卡式带收藏家提供全新体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275366" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_03-694x438.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="438" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_03-694x438.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_03.jpg 1045w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://direct.sanwa.co.jp/ItemAttr/400-MEDI050">SANWA</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/15/japanese-bluetooth-cassette/wireless-home/audio-visual/">日本推出多功能蓝牙 Cassette 机，可听收音机、转录 Cassette 带成 MP3</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
